{ This seems like the better recapture, but it is not often played. } 6... Nc6
{ Developing and attacking the d4-Queen. } 7. Qe4 g6
{ 7...d6  and  7...d5  are equally playable, but I have a personal preference for the fianchetto. }
8. Nc3 { Simple development from both sides follows. } 8... Bg7 9. Be2 d6
{ ...Qxd6-Bf5 will follow with an option of short or long castling according to your preference. }
